{"text_id":232365,"tokens":["Qu","asic","ry","stals",","," with"," their"," unique"," structural"," properties",","," have"," been"," a"," subject"," of"," significant"," interest"," in"," the"," field"," of"," materials"," science","."," In"," particular",","," Al","-","Pd","-","Mn"," quas","ic","ry","stals"," and"," their"," Xi","-","appro","xim","ants"," have"," been"," extensively"," studied"," due"," to"," their"," promising"," technological"," applications","."," However",","," a"," unified"," theoretical"," framework"," for"," describing"," the"," deformation"," mechanisms"," in"," these"," materials"," has"," yet"," to"," be"," established","."," In"," this"," work",","," we"," propose"," a"," projection"," formalism"," for"," describing"," the"," deformation"," behavior"," of"," Al","-","Pd","-","Mn"," quas","ic","ry","stals"," and"," their"," Xi","-","appro","xim","ants",","," with"," a"," focus"," on"," meta","dis","locations",".","\n\n","The"," proposed"," formalism"," is"," based"," on"," the"," concept"," of"," a"," Cut"," and"," Project"," Scheme"," (","CPS","),"," which"," allows"," for"," the"," description"," of"," both"," quas","ic","ry","stalline"," and"," approxim","ant"," structures"," within"," a"," single"," framework","."," By"," utilizing"," the"," CPS",","," we"," are"," able"," to"," describe"," the"," formation"," and"," motion"," of"," meta","dis","locations"," in"," a"," consistent"," manner",","," providing"," a"," unified"," understanding"," of"," deformation"," mechanisms"," in"," these"," materials",".","\n\n","The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," for"," a"," comprehensive"," theoretical"," understanding"," of"," quas","ic","ry","stalline"," materials",","," which"," can"," inform"," the"," development"," of"," new"," technologies"," and"," applications","."," The"," proposed"," projection"," formalism"," provides"," a"," foundation"," for"," future"," studies"," in"," this"," field",","," enabling"," the"," prediction"," of"," deformation"," behavior"," and"," the"," design"," of"," materials"," with"," tailored"," properties",".","\n\n","In"," summary",","," this"," work"," presents"," a"," unified"," projection"," formalism"," for"," the"," description"," of"," Al","-","Pd","-","Mn"," quas","ic","ry","stals"," and"," their"," Xi","-","appro","xim","ants",","," highlighting"," the"," crucial"," role"," of"," meta","dis","locations"," in"," their"," deformation"," behavior","."," The"," proposed"," formalism"," provides"," a"," significant"," step"," towards"," a"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," quas","ic","ry","stalline"," materials",","," paving"," the"," way"," for"," future"," technological"," advancements","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}